name: OrangeCloudLuxembourg
0:
”Alexa launch orange cloud”
”Alexa ask orange cloud for my picture of the day”
”Alexa ask orange cloud for my recent videos”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: orange cloud
Developer Terms of Use
des:
The Orange Cloud Luxembourg skill allows you to view pictures and videos from your cloud.orange.lu account. You can ask to show the picture of the day or the most recent pictures and videos.
All of your stuff will remain saved in cloud.
To start just link your cloud.orange.lu account.
This skill allows users to ask for:
* Picture of the day
* Most recent pictures
* Most recent videos
